{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 1531326, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 301847, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "最后这个太真实了可", "timestamp": 1619379144, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1531336, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 301847, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "二元论本质是个人信息处理能力有限的结果。\n反正只要就贝叶斯的方式来看某一有A特征的群体有更高的概率有B的负面特征，只要这个概率足够高，哪怕A完全不是B的原因，我照样“歧视”那些有A特性的群体。\n（当然要是我能够有信息处理能力处理并区分出B特性，那我显然就不会“歧视”了。因此虽然会地图炮，但对群体中的熟悉个体往往“歧视”比例会小很多", "timestamp": 1619379770, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1531551, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 301847, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "人上院系和人下院系呢？", "timestamp": 1619397863, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1531988, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 301847, "reply_to": 1531336, "tag": null, "text": "最后一句可太真实了", "timestamp": 1619404468, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1532442, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 301847, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "为什么HR要区分是否有房呢…简历也不写这个；还有户口也是", "timestamp": 1619408113, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1534343, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 301847, "reply_to": 1532442, "tag": null, "text": "Re Eve: 我培养你几年，你最后因为没房卷铺盖走人，企业很亏的", "timestamp": 1619422398, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1534346, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 301847, "reply_to": 1532442, "tag": null, "text": "Re Eve: 有些企业是分户口的呀，你没户口相当于多占了指标呀", "timestamp": 1619422417, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1534358, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 301847, "reply_to": 1531336, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 其实应聘者都差不多，都是些螺丝钉（当然大神除外），选谁不是选，那当然选个硬条件更好的了。斗士要进企业培养的，咱们那点学生经验根本不够看", "timestamp": 1619422529, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted"